{"tid":2216904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國海鮮含汞砷　俄羅斯正式決定禁止進口。俄餐廳老闆：不會再向中國入貨，不想毒害客戶","createTime":"2020-09-25T05:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T03:25:56.000Z","uid":273218,"like":136,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea9d1febb4e5f84130cdaeaf9d56e01b0018785","tid":2216904,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:14:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ren.tv/news/v-rossii/645981-so-rtutiu-i-myshiakom-rf-vremenno-ogranichila-vvoz-ryby-iz-knr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fren.tv%2Fnews%2Fv-rossii%2F645981-so-rtutiu-i-myshiakom-rf-vremenno-ogranichila-vvoz-ryby-iz-knr&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=313b8e79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ren.tv/news/v-rossii/645981-so-rtutiu-i-myshiakom-rf-vremenno-ogranichila-vvoz-ryby-iz-knr</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pourquoi.tw/2020/01/20/intlnews-russian-200112-200118-5/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pourquoi.tw%2F2020%2F01%2F20%2Fintlnews-russian-200112-200118-5%2Famp%2F&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=1a10b42d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pourquoi.tw/2020/01/20/intlnews-russian-200112-200118-5/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://rg.ru/2020/01/21/reg-ufo/kak-budet-razvivatsia-akvakultura-iuga-rossii-v-2020-godu.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frg.ru%2F2020%2F01%2F21%2Freg-ufo%2Fkak-budet-razvivatsia-akvakultura-iuga-rossii-v-2020-godu.html&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=10383148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rg.ru/2020/01/21/reg-ufo/kak-budet-razvivatsia-akvakultura-iuga-rossii-v-2020-godu.html</a><br />\n（By Google translate)<br />\n羅斯托夫餐廳的共同所有人安德烈&middot;科羅廖夫（Andrei Korolev）評論說：&ldquo;我從事餐廳業務已經很多年了，一直以來，水產養殖產品的價格都越來越昂貴，所以我們並不陌生。&rdquo; -我們以每公斤一千盧布的價格買了一個扇貝，今天是三盧布。他們要價2.5萬美元購買中文，許多人決定從中文購買。一切都比它們便宜：牡蠣，蝦，蟹肉，羅非魚，st魚和鰻魚。但是，與此同時，氣味是特定的，味道還有很多不足之處。而且，在俄羅斯農業和食品安全監管部門（Rosselkhoznadzor）的專家在其中一些產品中發現了砷和汞後，我們當然會完全放棄它們。而且，無論禁令是否延長。<span class=\"red\">即使中國製造商找到了解決方法，我們也不會向他們購買，因為我們不想毒害我們的客戶。</span>不再是價格了 但是在人們的信任下，因為許多牡蠣或魚類被訂購，希望這對身體有益。我認為我們會找到中國產品的替代品。"},{"pid":"04e07d3c7e267eacffccf6d110e3f5de3aa27eeb","tid":2216904,"uid":273218,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"最近好多報道養殖挪威三文魚問題<br />\n但鄰國養魚問題無咩本地傳媒講<br />\n甚至俄羅斯禁止進口都完全無聽過"},{"pid":"7537bea4834e146436ae93a530ab57569d949779","tid":2216904,"uid":109706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:18:01.000Z","msg":"push,"},{"pid":"1f7d0e01b02b57b53cc96fbacda2880e428c6b6a","tid":2216904,"uid":251732,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:24:45.000Z","msg":"Сука блядь КИТАЙСКИЙ"},{"pid":"5a8490e53c664f023a891e152991ec826899d8ed","tid":2216904,"uid":123869,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:42:18.000Z","msg":"我有批好靚ge扇貝"},{"pid":"79b31249664c7d5fa901366874d6c35b246c25e5","tid":2216904,"uid":273218,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"食物安全問題非常嚴峻<br />\n<br />\n其實同閆博士係反映緊一個現像<br />\n<br />\n世上需要更多吹肖者<br />\n<br />\n社會先會進步"},{"pid":"e44b7f6c08933cd0b772760a2a145553b946cd8b","tid":2216904,"uid":238370,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:56:38.000Z","msg":"契哥送完毒豬之後反手唔要契弟啲海鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bf5656f21f222a2576218382d69dc46002d9a6","tid":2216904,"uid":282637,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"即使中國製造商找到了解決方法，我們也不會向他們購買，因為我們不想毒害我們的客戶。<br />\n<br />\n中國商人:我有興趣買<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80bcc4be3a48299f2cca1be28b970e11e700d04f","tid":2216904,"uid":197149,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"俄國禁中國: 表示理解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" c